  "text": "Images were acquired using Leica SP5, Zeiss LSM700, and Zeiss LSM780 confocal microscopes with 40x or 63x water immersion objectives. Unless stated otherwise, images are single optical slices. Image quantifications were performed using Fiji [CITATION_1] , applying a double blind protocol where appropriate.",
